    <item>
      <title>英特尔任命两名临时联席首席执行官取代基辛格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/intel-replaces-gelsinger-with-two-interim-co-ceos-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司首席执行官帕特·基辛格在试图带领这家标志性芯片制造商扭亏为盈后辞职。英特尔首席财务官大卫·津斯纳和米歇尔·约翰斯顿·霍尔索斯将担任临时联席首席执行官，董事会将寻找继任者。彭博情报的 Mandeep Singh 正在主持“彭博未平仓合约”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/intel-replaces-gelsinger-with-two-interim-co-ceos-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:50:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗的 Kaiser 表示，就业和美联储将在年底前推动股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/jobs-fed-to-boost-stocks-into-year-s-end-citi-s-kaiser-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗银行美国股票交易策略主管斯图尔特·凯泽 (Stuart Kaiser) 预计，受就业数据和美联储再次降息的推动，股市将在年底前继续上涨。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/jobs-fed-to-boost-stocks-into-year-s-end-citi-s-kaiser-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:43:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑色星期五延伸至周末及以后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/black-friday-expands-into-the-weekend-and-beyond-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Telsey 咨询集团的 Dana Telsey 表示，大型零售商的折扣率约为 30%。她说，黑色星期五周末表现最好的零售商包括维多利亚的秘密、沃尔玛和 Hollister。她参加了“彭博监视”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-02/black-friday-expands-into-the-weekend-and-beyond-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:39:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储发言人称市场为大数据周做准备，美国国债价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/treasuries-drop-as-market-braces-for-big-data-week-fed-speakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债价格周一下跌，因为交易员们等待本周的大量经济数据和美联储高层官员的讲话，这些可能会决定人们对美联储本月下一步政策决定的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/treasuries-drop-as-market-braces-for-big-data-week-fed-speakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波罗的海航空公司已制定安全后返回乌克兰的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/airbaltic-has-ready-made-plan-to-fly-back-into-ukraine-once-safe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波罗的海航空公司表示，该公司已制定计划，在乌克兰空域重新开放后短时间内恢复飞往乌克兰的航班。三年前，俄罗斯入侵导致乌克兰空中交通中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/airbaltic-has-ready-made-plan-to-fly-back-into-ukraine-once-safe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:26:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将美元武器化被视为对金砖国家的无谓挑衅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/trump-weaponizing-dollar-seen-as-a-needless-brics-provocation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场观察人士表示，唐纳德·特朗普向世界各国施加新压力，要求其维持以美元为基础的金融体系，这种策略可能会适得其反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/trump-weaponizing-dollar-seen-as-a-needless-brics-provocation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:46:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
